{"tid":2274903,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"卡牌遊戲仙劍奇俠傳九野(steam)","createTime":"2020-11-06T17:50:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T06:06:29.000Z","uid":41414,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6a41db19d8a82db2703802644f06e23c06a51326","tid":2274903,"uid":41414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T17:50:59.000Z","msg":"醜話說在前頭<br />\n大宇雖然係台灣公司<br />\n但有中資 而且呢隻遊戲暫時得殘體<br />\n不喜請負皮<br />\n<br />\n出左幾日<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oAXc3Kw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoAXc3Kw.jpg&h=653b278a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YKKZJKx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYKKZJKx.jpg&h=f7adb8c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劇情係同類型遊戲中比較長<br />\n寫得都唔錯 算係王道類型<br />\n當佢免費單機驚玩已經幾好<br />\n送野都幾良心 而且除左主線有仙劍一代篇<br />\n暫時覺得都幾平衡<br />\n肯打哂每日任務唔洗點課金都得<br />\n有興趣就一齊玩下<br />\n反正唔洗錢 而且亦都唔係抄皮卡牌遊戲<br />\n系統幾特別"},{"pid":"af75daa0173b892bed8b390ca3b418f45e261e27","tid":2274903,"uid":41414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T06:06:29.000Z","msg":"有冇人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}